{"type": "article", "id": 17432, "title": "椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-12T06:43:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 75, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122433S9DBTPhOabUtHd30.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这一系列的木质座椅来自日本产品设计师小池和也（Kazuya Koike），它们正在东京设计周的“材料设计展”上展出。他将成组的薄木被切成条形，经过染色后贴在一起组成了颜色明快的渐变色椅子。椅子的材料用了浅色的枫木，经过染色后仍然保留了自然的花纹。这其实是一个关于材料的实验，如果推广后将会有更多的颜色搭配。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261445475NOSitvcPwaQDYnA.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144547pXGCiHOYPJyR1wvn.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"460\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144547vGmCszWcAXw8Zby0.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726144548X9eCnlaKkysN2IOu.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"540\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6601467\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}